data.description:
Charming 4BR/3BA home in immaculate condition. Kitchen has granite counter tops, plenty of cabinets, gas stove, tile black splash, pendant lighting with top tier appliance package. Ceiling fans throughout. Home features engineered luxury vinyl plank flooring downstairs and carpet in bedroom upstairs. 
Wood stairs with iron handrail spindles, two -inch wood blinds, tankless hot water heater and a CPI system Smart House (controls lights, locks and thermostat from your phone. Large corner lot with full privacy fenced backyard. 12 x 20 screened porch with additional 8 x 10 patio plumbed for outdoor gas grill. Great location just minutes from North Augusta, Augusta and Aiken.
